      }, "The pioneer fishing trip was an all-camp party.  With but one steamer, everybody towed behind.  But now the fishing trip has become a rock dinner, starting before noon\u2014sometimes\u2014and caparisoned with cushions, camp chairs and card tables.  A few of the Mid-Victorians still fish, and enjoy it; but fishing is no longer de rigueur. \u201CO tempora, O mores!\u201D [Alas, for the times and the manners!]"), /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("p", {
