      }, "With all the comforts, even luxuries, of today, one characteristic of the first camp has persisted in its full vigor throughout our whole history.  Sunday is the Sabbath, whether at home or in camp.  From the first Sunday of the first camp there has never been an omission of the service of worship in camp on Sunday throughout the entire fifty years.  Our Club has a reputation throughout Canada for \u201Cremembering the Sabbath Day\u201D.  Under the shadow of these principles we have been preserved without a serious accident through all these years.  And we take a proper pride in maintaining these standards.")), /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement(Container, {
